TY  - JOUR
TI  - External Diseconomies in Consumption and Monopoly Pricing
AU  - Luski, Israel
AU  - Lusky, Rafael
AB  - [This paper deals with the relationship between the monopoly price and the socially optimal price in the presence of consumption diseconomies. The above relationship is derived from characteristics of the utility function.]
