TY  - JOUR
TI  - Wealth Effects and Slutsky Equations for Assets
AU  - Epps, Thomas W.
AB  - [Changes in asset prices are shown to produce only substitution effects in a broad class of portfolio-choice models. Wealth effects are identically zero unless the individual's stocks of assets are subject to unanticipated changes.]
