TY  - JOUR
TI  - Gram-Charlier Approximations Applied to t Ratios of k-Class Estimators
AU  - Sargan, J. D.
AB  - [This paper obtains Edgeworth or Gram-Charlier expansions for the t ratio of instrumental variable and k-class estimators, and uses them to give approximations to the confidence intervals obtained from these t ratios. These confidence intervals for large sample size are more accurate than the usual asymptotic confidence interval.]
